Text_DreamEaterWhichMon::
	.string "哪一只宝可梦想要学会\n"
	.string "食梦呢？$"

Text_DreamEaterTaught::
	.string "……ZZZ……\n"
	.string "我……实在是……吃不下了……$"

PewterCity_Text_ClefairyCameFromMoon::
	.string "有这样一个传说，\n"
	.string "说皮皮来自月亮。\p"
	.string "在那之后月之石\n"
	.string "才出现在了月见山。$"

PewterCity_Text_BrockOnlySeriousTrainerHere::
	.string "这里没有那种很严肃的\n"
	.string "宝可梦训练家。\p"
	.string "他们都打扮得像个捉虫少年，\n"
	.string "你懂的，就是一种癖好。\p"
	.string "可深灰道馆的小刚并不像这样打扮。\n"
	.string "不像，一点都不像。$"

PewterCity_Text_DidYouCheckOutMuseum::
	.string "你去博物馆看过了吗？$"

PewterCity_Text_WerentThoseFossilsAmazing::
	.string "不觉得这些来自月见山的化石\n"
	.string "很令人吃惊吗？$"

PewterCity_Text_ReallyYouHaveToGo::
	.string "真的？\n"
	.string "你必须得去一次看看！$"

PewterCity_Text_ThisIsTheMuseum::
	.string "博物馆就在这里了。\p"
	.string "虽然你必须花钱买了票才能进去，\n"
	.string "但是里面非常值得一看。回头见！$"

PewterCity_Text_DoYouKnowWhatImDoing::
	.string "嘘！\n"
	.string "你知道我正在做什么吗？$"

PewterCity_Text_ThatsRightItsHardWork::
	.string "没错！\n"
	.string "这事做起来可不轻松！$"

PewterCity_Text_SprayingRepelToKeepWildMonsOut::
	.string "我正在喷除虫喷雾使那些野生的\n"
	.string "宝可梦远离我的花园！$"

PewterCity_Text_BrocksLookingForChallengersFollowMe::
	.string "你是一个训练家，对吗？\p"
	.string "小刚正在寻找新的挑战者\n"
	.string "跟我来！$"

PewterCity_Text_GoTakeOnBrock::
	.string "如果你有了正确的信念，\n"
	.string "就应该去打倒小刚！$"

PewterCity_Text_TrainerTipsEarningEXP::
	.string "训练家贴士\p"
	.string "在战斗中出场过的宝可梦，\n"
	.string "哪怕是只打了瓶酱油都会获得经验值。$"

PewterCity_Text_CallPoliceIfInfoOnThieves::
	.string "通知\p"
	.string "有些小偷正在对月见山的\n"
	.string "宝可梦化石下手。\p"
	.string "如果你有任何线索\n"
	.string "请马上通知深灰警察局。$"

PewterCity_Text_MuseumOfScience::
	.string "深灰科学博物馆$"

PewterCity_Text_GymSign::
	.string "深灰市宝可梦道馆\n"
	.string "馆主：小刚\l"
	.string "有如磐石般坚硬的宝可梦训练家！$"

PewterCity_Text_CitySign::
	.string "深灰市\n"
	.string "灰色的岩石之城$"

PewterCity_Text_OhPlayer::
	.string "噢，{PLAYER}{KUN}！$"

PewterCity_Text_AskedToDeliverThis::
	.string "能够赶上你真高兴。\n"
	.string "我是大木博士的助手。\p"
	.string "给。\n"
	.string "我被叮嘱要把这件东西带给你。$"

PewterCity_Text_ReceivedRunningShoesFromAide::
	.string "{PLAYER}从助手那里\n"
	.string "获得了跑步鞋。$"

PewterCity_Text_SwitchedShoesWithRunningShoes::
	.string "{PLAYER}换上了\n"
	.string "跑步鞋。$"

PewterCity_Text_ExplainRunningShoes::
	.string "现在开始按B键就可以跑步了。\n"
	.string "但是只能在空旷的地方跑哦！$"

PewterCity_Text_MustBeGoingBackToLab::
	.string "那么，我必须回\n"
	.string "研究所去了。\p"
	.string "再见啦！$"

PewterCity_Text_RunningShoesLetterFromMom::
	.string "是一封信……\p"
	.string "亲爱的{PLAYER}，\p"
	.string "这双跑步鞋\n"
	.string "是给我心爱的挑战者的。\p"
	.string "我一直都会祝福你。\n"
	.string "记住，永远不要中途就放弃了！\p"
	.string "妈妈$"

